messages.message: Not sure if anyone else sees this but occasionally (~50%) of the time, when I load the aihub page for the first time all the text is rendered in some serif font for a couple of seconds before it switches to our actual font. Is this expected? It’s too fast for me to capture in a video.
I just put up a PR that will make us load many less fonts, so let’s see if that makes it better at all…
